Your third Anſwer is; The people have Judicium diſcretionis, you grant, not of Order and Method, to direct and determine that; 
               Pag. 36. 
               this is proper to the Miniſter. We are, Sir, in this agreed; but your fancy doth confound the medium cultus with the modus miniſterialis; the laſt you will not allow, and the firſt you do not underſtand; there is the reaſon of the ſtrife: I pray you, Sir, ſtudy the propriety of theſe terms in reference to Gods Worſhip; for want of this, you miſ-apply Zanchy and all other Authors.
